title: Model Irina Shayk says social media 'perfection' causes pressure
text:
Model Irina Shayk says social media 'perfection' causes pressure Monday, April 23, 2018 - 01:50 
The Russian model, at the launch of Pronovias' new new bridal collection showcase, says size does not matter as long as you love your body. Rough cut (No reporter narration).
